{"meta":{"title":"Libraries & Add-ons","description":"Collection of libraries and addons that work well with Preact"},"html":"<h1>Libraries & Add-ons</h1><p>A collection of modules built to work wonderfully with Preact.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>ğŸ’ <em>Built one of your own?\n<a href=\"https://github.com/preactjs/preact-www/blob/master/content/en/about/libraries-addons.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Add it!</a></em></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n\t\t\t\t<h2 id=\"add-ons\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"fragment-link\" href=\"#add-ons\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-label=\"Link to: Add-Ons (#add-ons)\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<use href=\"/icons.svg#link\" ></use>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</svg>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>Add-Ons</span>\n\t\t\t\t</h2><ul>\n<li>ğŸ” <a href=\"https://github.com/developit/preact-cycle\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-cycle**</a>: Functional-reactive paradigm for Preact</li>\n<li>ğŸ“„ <a href=\"https://github.com/preactjs/preact-render-to-string\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-render-to-string**</a>: Universal rendering.</li>\n<li>â² <a href=\"https://github.com/trambarhq/relaks\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**relaks**</a>: Create components with render methods that return asynchronously.</li>\n<li>ğŸ”© <a href=\"https://github.com/edwjusti/express-preact-views\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**express-preact-views**</a>: Express View Engine.</li>\n<li>ğŸ’¾ <a href=\"https://github.com/JoviDeCroock/prefresh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**Prefresh**</a>: Fast-Refresh for Preact.</li>\n<li>ğŸ“‘ <a href=\"https://github.com/DonsWayo/adonis-preact\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**adonis-preact**</a>: Use Preact in Adonisjs</li>\n</ul>\n\n\t\t\t\t<h2 id=\"components\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"fragment-link\" href=\"#components\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-label=\"Link to: Components (#components)\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<use href=\"/icons.svg#link\" ></use>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</svg>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>Components</span>\n\t\t\t\t</h2><ul>\n<li>ğŸŒ <a href=\"https://github.com/preactjs/preact-router\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-router**</a>: URL routing for your components</li>\n<li>ğŸ“‘ <a href=\"https://github.com/developit/preact-markup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-markup**</a>: Render HTML &amp; Custom Elements as JSX &amp; Components</li>\n<li>ğŸ›° <a href=\"https://github.com/developit/preact-portal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-portal**</a>: Render Preact components into (a) SPACE ğŸŒŒ</li>\n<li>ğŸ“ <a href=\"https://github.com/developit/preact-richtextarea\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-richtextarea**</a>: Simple HTML editor component</li>\n<li>ğŸ”– <a href=\"https://github.com/developit/preact-token-input\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-token-input**</a>: Text field that tokenizes input, for things like tags</li>\n<li>ğŸ“‡ <a href=\"https://github.com/developit/preact-virtual-list\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-virtual-list**</a>: Easily render lists with millions of rows (<a href=\"https://jsfiddle.net/developit/qqan9pdo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">demo</a>)</li>\n<li>ğŸ“ <a href=\"https://download.github.io/preact-layout/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-layout**</a>: Small and simple layout library</li>\n<li>ğŸ‘· <a href=\"https://github.com/download/preact-helmet\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-helmet**</a>: A document head manager for Preact</li>\n<li>â†• <a href=\"https://github.com/lucafalasco/preact-custom-scrollbars\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-custom-scrollbars**</a>: Fully customizable scrollbars, for frictionless native browser scrolling</li>\n<li>ğŸ§± <a href=\"https://modularforms.dev/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**@modular-forms/preact**</a>: Modular and type-safe form library</li>\n</ul>\n\n\t\t\t\t<h2 id=\"integrations\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"fragment-link\" href=\"#integrations\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-label=\"Link to: Integrations (#integrations)\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<use href=\"/icons.svg#link\" ></use>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</svg>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>Integrations</span>\n\t\t\t\t</h2><ul>\n<li>ğŸ’­ <a href=\"https://github.com/matthewmueller/preact-socrates\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-socrates**</a>: Preact plugin for <a href=\"http://github.com/matthewmueller/socrates\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Socrates</a></li>\n<li>ğŸš£ <a href=\"https://github.com/xialvjun/preact-flyd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-flyd**</a>: Use <a href=\"https://github.com/paldepind/flyd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">flyd</a> FRP streams in Preact + JSX</li>\n<li>ğŸ’¬ <a href=\"https://github.com/download/preact-i18nline\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-i18nline**</a>: Integrates the ecosystem around <a href=\"https://github.com/everydayhero/i18n-js\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">i18n-js</a> with Preact via <a href=\"https://github.com/download/i18nline\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">i18nline</a>.</li>\n<li>ğŸ’  <a href=\"https://capacitorjs.com/solution/preact\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**Capacitor**</a>: Turn your Preact app into a Native iOS/Android App and PWA.</li>\n<li>:ice_cube: <a href=\"https://kretes.dev/docs/howtos/preact-setup/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**Kretes**</a>: Build full-stack TypeScript apps using Preact and Node.js</li>\n<li>ğŸ: <a href=\"https://github.com/mwood23/preact-island\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-island**</a>: Run your Preact widget on any website with reactive props.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\t\t\t\t<h2 id=\"gui-toolkits\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"fragment-link\" href=\"#gui-toolkits\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-label=\"Link to: GUI Toolkits (#gui-toolkits)\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<use href=\"/icons.svg#link\" ></use>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</svg>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>GUI Toolkits</span>\n\t\t\t\t</h2><ul>\n<li>ğŸ´ <a href=\"https://github.com/mui/material-ui/tree/master/examples/material-ui-preact\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**@mui/material**</a>: the React UI library you always wanted. Follow your own design system, or start with Material Design.</li>\n<li>ğŸ‘ <a href=\"https://github.com/prateekbh/preact-material-components\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-material-components**</a>: Material Components for the Web (supersedes MDL)</li>\n<li>ğŸ”³ <a href=\"https://github.com/developit/preact-mdl\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-mdl**</a>: Use <a href=\"https://getmdl.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">MDL</a> as Preact components</li>\n<li>ğŸš€ <a href=\"https://github.com/developit/preact-photon\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-photon**</a>: build beautiful desktop UI with <a href=\"http://photonkit.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">photon</a></li>\n<li>ğŸ§ <a href=\"https://github.com/afeiship/preact-weui\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-weui**</a>: <a href=\"https://github.com/afeiship/preact-weui\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Weui</a> for Preact</li>\n<li>ğŸ’… <a href=\"https://github.com/ajainvivek/preact-fluid\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-fluid**</a>: <a href=\"https://github.com/ajainvivek/preact-fluid\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Fluid</a> minimal UI kit for Preact</li>\n<li>ğŸ“– <a href=\"https://github.com/storybooks/storybook/tree/next/app/preact\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**storybook-preact**</a>: Storybook for Preact is a UI development environment for your Preact components</li>\n</ul>\n\n\t\t\t\t<h3 id=\"testing\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"fragment-link\" href=\"#testing\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-label=\"Link to: Testing (#testing)\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<use href=\"/icons.svg#link\" ></use>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</svg>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>Testing</span>\n\t\t\t\t</h3><ul>\n<li>ğŸ”¬ <a href=\"https://github.com/developit/preact-jsx-chai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-jsx-chai**</a>: JSX assertion testing <em>(no DOM, right in Node)</em></li>\n<li>âœ… <a href=\"https://github.com/bruderstein/unexpected-preact\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**unexpected-preact**</a>: JSX assertions, events, snapshots in Jest <em>(DOM, works under Node jsdom or out-of-the-box in Jest)</em> - <a href=\"https://bruderstein.github.io/unexpected-preact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">docs</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\t\t\t\t<h2 id=\"utilities\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"fragment-link\" href=\"#utilities\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-label=\"Link to: Utilities (#utilities)\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<use href=\"/icons.svg#link\" ></use>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</svg>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>Utilities</span>\n\t\t\t\t</h2><ul>\n<li>ğŸ© <a href=\"https://github.com/ld0rman/preact-classless-component\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-classless-component**</a>: create preact components without the class keyword</li>\n<li>ğŸ”¨ <a href=\"https://github.com/queckezz/preact-hyperscript\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**preact-hyperscript**</a>: Hyperscript-like syntax for creating elements</li>\n<li>âœ… <a href=\"https://github.com/tkh44/shallow-compare\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**shallow-compare**</a>: simplified <code>shouldComponentUpdate</code> helper.</li>\n<li>ğŸ“¶ <a href=\"https://github.com/EthanStandel/deepsignal/tree/main/packages/preact\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">**@deepsignal/preact**</a>: Extension of <code>@preact/signals</code> for full state management</li>\n</ul>\n"}